
Customer
Register-1
URL: /api/customer
Method: POST
Request:
  - username: string
  - password: string
  - email: string
  - hint: string
  - hint_answer: string
Register a new customer. If success, return 201 Created.
Login-1
URL: /api/customer/login
Method: POST
Request:
  - username: string
  - password: string
Use the username and password to login. If the username and password are correct, return a JWT token.
{
  "token": "string"
}
Get customer info
URL: /api/customer/info
Method: GET
Header:
  - token: string
Get the customer info. If success, return 200 OK.
{
  "username": "string",
  "email": "string",
  "hint": "string"
}
Update customer info
URL: /api/customer/info
Method: PUT
Header:
  - token: string
Request:
  - email: string
  - hint: string
  - hint_answer: string
Update the customer info. If success, return 200 OK.
