Product
Get product list
URL: /api/products/<int:page>
Method: GET
Get the product list. If success, return 200 OK.
{
  "products": [
    {
      "id": "int",
      "name": "string",
      "price": "float",
      "description": "string",
      "image": "string",
      "seller": "string"
    }
  ],
  "total": "int",
  "pages": "int"
}
Get product detail
URL: /api/product/<int:id>
Method: GET
Get the product detail. If success, return 200 OK.
{
  "id": "int",
  "name": "string",
  "price": "float",
  "description": "string",
  "image": "string",
  "seller": "string"
}
Create product
URL: /api/product
Method: POST
Header:
  - token: string
Request:
  - name: string
  - price: float
  - description: string
  - image: string # base64 encoded
Create a new product. If success, return 201 Created.
Update product
URL: /api/product/<int:id>
Method: PUT
Header:
  - token: string
Request:
  - name: string
  - price: float
  - description: string
  - image: string
Update the product. If success, return 200 OK.
Delete product
URL: /api/product/<int:id>
Method: DELETE
Header:
  - token: string
Delete the product. If success, return 200 OK.
When there are orders related to the product, the product will not be deleted.
Order
Get order list
URL: /api/orders/<int:page>
Method: GET
Header:
  - token: string
Get the order list (of the current customer or seller). If success, return 200 OK.
{
  "orders": [
    {
      "id": "int",
      "product": "string",
      "customer": "string",
      "quantity": "int",
      "total": "float",
      "status": "string",
      "created_at": "string"
    }
  ],
  "total": "int",
  "pages": "int"
}
Get order detail
URL: /api/order/<int:id>
Method: GET
Header:
  - token: string
Get the order detail (of the current customer or seller). If success, return 200 OK.
{
  "id": "int",
  "product": "string",
  "customer": "string",
  "quantity": "int",
  "total": "float",
  "address": "string",
  "status": "string",
  "created_at": "string"
}
Create order
URL: /api/order
Method: POST
Header:
  - token: string
Request:
  - product: int
  - quantity: int
  - address: string
Create a new order. If success, return 201 Created.
Update order
URL: /api/order/<int:id>
Method: PUT
Header:
  - token: string
Request:
  - status: string
Update the order. If success, return 200 OK.
Delete order
URL: /api/order/<int:id>
Method: DELETE
Header:
  - token: string
Delete the order (only if the order is completed, or cancelled). If success, return 200 OK.
Cart
Get cart
URL: /api/cart
Method: GET
Header:
  - token: string
Get the cart. If success, return 200 OK.
{
  "products": [
    {
      "id": "int",
      "product": "int",
      "quantity": "int"
    }
  ],
  "total": "float"
}
Add product to cart
URL: /api/cart
Method: POST
Header:
  - token: string
Request:
  - product: int
  - quantity: int
Add a product to the cart. If success, return 201 Created.
Update product in cart
URL: /api/cart/<int:id>
Method: PUT
Header:
  - token: string
Request:
  - quantity: int
Update the product in the cart. If success, return 200 OK.
Delete product in cart
URL: /api/cart/<int:id>
Method: DELETE
Header:
  - token: string
Delete the product in the cart. If success, return 200 OK.
